title: Samrup Jay
description: Small restaurant with a sign at the front that reads "Pure Vegetarian Vegan." Menu is in Thai and in English; some English spoken. Previously located on Si Samphet Road and named Ahan Jay Si Samphet. Location is opposite Ayutthaya Business Administration Technical College on U-Thong Road, near U-Thong Soi 25 which is signposted; there is also a red and yellow Youta Vegetarian Food sign at the front as well as the little triangular yellow and red flags signifying vegetarian food.
